short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: THIS EXTENSION IS FOR BETA TESTING. Create a ClickUp task from a Dice candidate

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension allows you to to create a ClickUp tasks representing a candidate using the following data: team_id (workspace), list_id, email custom field id, and Dice profile custom field id.
